description.en: Tr3zor is an app that provides access to the global blockchain-based database of lost and stolen items allowing users to find their belongings. Tr3 is the native utility token that is used for: posting lost and found items; distributing and receiving rewards for helping users to return their funds. The app is based on the image recognition technology and blockchain to provide reliable service for searching lost belongings.
